ng Huynh|Huynh]]</small> *''[[Pandanus tricolor]]'' <small>[[Harold St. John|H.St.John]]</small> *''[[Pandanus tsaratananensis]]'' <small>[[Ugolino Martelli|Martelli]]</small> *''[[Pandanus tsingycola]]'' <small>[[Callm.]] & [[Nusb.]]</small> *''[[Pandanus tubulatus]]'' <small>[[Kim-Lang Huynh|Huynh]]</small> *''[[Pandanus turbinatus]]'' <small>[[Conrad Loddiges|Lodd.]] ex [[Ernst Gottlieb von Steudel|Steud.]]</small> *''[[Pandanus turritus]]'' <small>[[Ugolino Martelli|Martelli]]</small> *''[[Pandanus tutuilaensis]]'' <small>[[Ugolino Martelli|Martelli]]</small> {{div col end}}
