rk | [[Norrbotten County]] | {{sort|{{commas|11000}}|{{convert|11000|ha|acre|0|sigfig=2|abbr=on}}}} | TBA |- !scope=row|[[Rogen (lake)|Rogen]]-Juttulslätten National Park | [[Dalarna County]] and [[Jämtland County]] | {{sort|{{commas|100000}}|{{convert|100000|ha|acre|0|sigfig=2|abbr=on}}}} | TBA |- !scope=row|Sankt Anna National Park | [[Östergötland County]] | {{sort|{{commas|10000}}|{{convert|10000|ha|acre|0|sigfig=2|abbr=on}}}} | TBA |- !scope=row|Vindelfjällen National Park | [[Västerbotten County]] | {{sort|{{commas|550000}}|{{convert|550000|ha|acre|0|sigfig=2|abbr=on}}}} | TBA |}
